# Company Overview

## General Information & Overview

### Who We Are

The **Alamo Prime Brand** brings hustle, creativity and passion to our work. This culture shows up in every plate, glass, high-five and guest interaction. We thrive under pressure, welcome challenges, overcome obstacles ‚Äî and above all, we have a great time. 

> **üí° Our Identity**: We are a collection of mavericks and misfits; to those who have the same passion for Food & Beverage that we do ‚Äî **welcome home!!**

### Our Founder Story

#### The Vision Behind Alamo Prime

**Marlon Tapanes**, a seasoned hospitality veteran with over a decade of experience across luxury restaurants and premium dining concepts, envisioned a revolutionary approach to the modern steakhouse experience. After managing operations for renowned brands like Fox Restaurant Concepts, Hilton Hotels, and luxury establishments in Miami, Las Vegas, and Dallas, Marlon identified a crucial gap in the market: fine dining that was both exceptional and approachable.

#### The Los Alamos Inspiration

In 2008, while immersed in San Antonio's vibrant culinary scene, Marlon discovered the profound influence of the Alamo on the city's culture and identity. The Alamo represents more than just a landmark‚Äîit embodies **American courage, relentless pursuit of excellence, and unwavering determination**. These values resonated deeply with Marlon's own hospitality philosophy and became the cornerstone of Alamo Prime's foundation.

Drawing inspiration from the nearby Los Alamos heritage, Marlon recognized that true excellence comes from honoring tradition while embracing innovation. The scientific precision and collaborative spirit of Los Alamos became the template for Alamo Prime's kitchen operations and guest service philosophy.

#### The Grandma's Kitchen Connection

Marlon's culinary journey began in his grandmother's kitchen, where he learned that exceptional food isn't about complexity‚Äîit's about **soul, quality, and the joy of bringing people together**. Those early experiences, filled with authentic flavors and genuine hospitality, shaped his belief that fine dining should feel like coming home.

This grandmother-inspired approach became the heart of Alamo Prime's menu‚Äîwhere modern techniques meet timeless comfort, and every dish tells a story of heritage and innovation.

#### Creating the New Standard

As an avid wine connoisseur and steak enthusiast, Marlon envisioned a restaurant where **premium fine dining meets approachable luxury**. Alamo Prime was born from this vision: a chic, trendy destination where white-collar professionals and discerning diners could experience Michelin-quality cuisine without the intimidating price tags or pretentious atmosphere.

The concept revolutionizes the traditional steakhouse by:
- **Modern Yet Approachable Design** - Sophisticated ambiance that welcomes everyone
- **Exceptional Quality, Fair Pricing** - Premium ingredients without the premium markup
- **Engaging Hospitality** - Where servers are knowledgeable hosts, not just order-takers
- **Wine Excellence** - Curated selections that impress both connoisseurs and newcomers

#### The San Antonio Renaissance

Marlon recognized that San Antonio was experiencing unprecedented investment and cultural growth. The city deserved a restaurant that matched its ambition while honoring its heritage. Alamo Prime became his contribution to this renaissance‚Äîa place where local pride meets global sophistication.

The restaurant embodies the spirit of modern San Antonio: **confident, innovative, and deeply connected to its roots**. Just as the Alamo stands as a testament to American resilience, Alamo Prime stands as a monument to culinary excellence and hospitality innovation.

#### Our Philosophy: Hospitality Redefined

At Alamo Prime, we believe that exceptional hospitality is about **connection, conversation, and creating moments**. Marlon's extensive experience taught him that the best dining experiences aren't just about the food‚Äîthey're about the stories shared, the relationships built, and the memories created.

Every element of Alamo Prime reflects this philosophy:
- **Engaging Service** - Our team are hosts who love talking about food and wine
- **Educational Experience** - Guests learn about their selections in an approachable way
- **Community Focus** - We're not just serving meals; we're building relationships
- **Continuous Innovation** - Like the pioneers of Los Alamos, we always push boundaries

#### The Future of Fine Dining

Under Marlon's leadership as Managing Partner of Identity Hospitality Group, Alamo Prime represents the future of fine dining‚Äî**sophisticated without being stuffy, premium without being pretentious, and exceptional without being exclusive**.

This is more than a restaurant; it's a movement to make world-class dining accessible to everyone who appreciates quality, craftsmanship, and genuine hospitality.

### About This Training Guide

As a member of the **Alamo Prime Food & Beverage** team, you will be a part of creating a unique and memorable bar & dining experience. You play an essential role in the success of our brand's future.

This guide provides useful information about your position so that you can offer professional, gracious, and friendly service to our guests. We want you to be successful and comfortable with the items discussed on the following pages because they will help you make the right decisions during service.

> **Remember, when in doubt: ASK** - Once you become comfortable in your new job, we welcome your input and suggestions so that we may improve our high standard of service. We appreciate the great experience and positive attitude that our team will bring. We look forward to working together to produce memorable moments for our guests.

### Our Expectations

You will be hired for your ability to fully invest in the job and exhibit a high level of professionalism at all times. You will be expected to maintain your knowledge of food, beer, wine, spirits, and service to the highest standard. This will allow you the tools to provide detailed service and have confidence in delivering an elevated service experience to all our guests.

---

## Brand Philosophy

### The Alamo Prime Experience

> **"The concept will offer an approachable dining experience in addition to an energy for those looking to gather with friends. The venue will offer a modern American Steak House cuisine while the energy will bring a moody and sexy vibe."**

### Our Commitment

At Alamo Prime, we are committed to:

- **Exceptional Food** - Modern American steakhouse with creative flair
- **Premium Beverages** - Craft cocktails and curated wine selection
- **Memorable Ambiance** - Moody, sexy, energetic atmosphere
- **Outstanding Service** - Professional, attentive, personalized

### Target Experience

We create experiences where guests can:
- **Gather with friends** in a vibrant atmosphere
- **Enjoy exceptional cuisine** prepared with passion
- **Savor premium beverages** crafted by experts
- **Create lasting memories** through outstanding hospitality

