#### Success Metrics
- **Guest satisfaction** scores for arrival experience
- **Reservation accuracy** and management
- **Wait time accuracy** and communication
- **Phone professionalism** metrics

### Service Department
**Primary Mission**: Exceptional dining experience and guest satisfaction

#### Key Responsibilities
- **Table Service** - Professional, attentive service throughout dining experience
- **Menu Knowledge** - Expert knowledge of menu items and recommendations
- **Sales Excellence** - Upselling and suggestive selling based on guest preferences
- **Guest Relationship** - Building rapport and recognizing returning guests
- **Problem Resolution** - Addressing guest concerns with ownership and professionalism
- **Team Collaboration** - Coordinated service with kitchen and bar

#### Success Metrics
- **Guest satisfaction** scores and feedback
- **Sales performance** and upselling effectiveness
- **Team collaboration** and communication
- **Service consistency** and standards adherence

### Bar Department
**Primary Mission**: Premium beverage service and bar guest experience

#### Key Responsibilities
- **Beverage Preparation** - Expertly crafted cocktails and drinks
- **Bar Guest Service** - Exceptional service for bar guests
- **Menu Knowledge** - Deep understanding of beverages and pairings
- **Inventory Management** - Proper stocking and waste reduction
- **Cleanliness and Organization** - Immaculate bar area and equipment
- **Compliance** - Responsible alcohol service and safety protocols

#### Success Metrics
- **Beverage quality** and presentation
- **Bar guest satisfaction** and experience
- **Sales performance** and upselling
- **Inventory control** and cost management

### Kitchen Department
**Primary Mission**: Culinary excellence and food quality

#### Key Responsibilities
- **Food Preparation** - Consistent, high-quality food execution
- **Menu Execution** - Perfect preparation of all menu items
- **Quality Control** - Maintaining highest food safety and quality standards
- **Kitchen Organization** - Clean, efficient, and safe kitchen environment
- **Timing and Coordination** - Synchronized food preparation with service
- **Menu Development** - Innovation and menu improvement contributions

#### Success Metrics
- **Food quality** and consistency
- **Ticket times** and kitchen efficiency
- **Food safety** and cleanliness standards
- **Team coordination** and communication

---

## Cross-Functional Collaboration

### Service Integration
- **Host-Server Communication** - Guest information and special requests
- **Server-Bar Coordination** - Drink orders and timing
- **Server-Kitchen Collaboration** - Food orders and special accommodations
- **All-Management Support** - Leadership guidance and problem resolution

### Team Synergy
