# Operational Procedures Overview

## Operations Framework

> **üí° Our Excellence**: At Alamo Prime, operational excellence is achieved through standardized procedures that ensure consistency, quality, and efficiency in every aspect of restaurant operations. Our procedures are designed to support the S.H.O.W. service framework while maintaining the highest standards of safety, cleanliness, and guest satisfaction.

---

## Procedure Categories

### Daily Operational Cycle
- **Opening Procedures**: Restaurant preparation and setup for service
