# Environment Standards

## Environment Framework

> **üí° Our Atmosphere**: At Alamo Prime, our environment is an essential component of the guest experience. First impressions are extremely important - from the appearance of the building to clean windows, doors, staff, lighting, and music, we must pay attention to all details to create the exceptional atmosphere our guests expect.

