## First Impressions Management

### The Importance of Environment
**First impressions set the tone** for the entire dining experience. Every visual and sensory element contributes to our guests' perception of quality, professionalism, and attention to detail.

#### Environmental Impact on Guest Experience
- **Visual Appeal**: Clean, well-maintained appearance signals quality
